```
classDiagram
    class LoanManagementApp {
        +main(String[] args)
    }
    
    class MainFrame {
        -CardLayout mainCardLayout
        +buildCustomerPortal()
        +buildEmployeePortal()
    }
    
    class SessionManager {
        <<Utility>>
        +login(userId, name, role)
        +getCurrentUserId()
    }
    
    class DatabaseConnection {
        <<Utility>>
        +getConnection() Connection
    }
    
    class LoginScreen {
        +handleLogin()
    }
    
    class CustomerScreens {
        <<Customer Portal>>
        CustomerDashboard
        ApplyLoanScreen
        LoanStatusScreen
        ProfileScreen
    }
    
    class EmployeeScreens {
        <<Employee Portal>>
        EmployeeDashboard
        ApprovalsScreen
        AllApplicationsScreen
        ReportsScreen
    }

    LoanManagementApp --> MainFrame : Launches
    MainFrame --> LoginScreen : Displays Initially
    LoginScreen ..> DatabaseConnection : Verifies User
    LoginScreen ..> SessionManager : Sets Active User
    MainFrame ..> SessionManager : Checks Role
    MainFrame --> CustomerScreens : Routes Customer
    MainFrame --> EmployeeScreens : Routes Employee
    CustomerScreens ..> DatabaseConnection : SQL Queries (CRUD)
    EmployeeScreens ..> DatabaseConnection : SQL Queries (CRUD)
```
